description.en: The DWS Protocol will utilize the NEO platform as a top-level partner on a level 1 Blockchain partnership. The DWS Protocol will utilize NEO’s Digital Asset functionality, Digital Identity module, dBFS Consensus Algorithm, and Delegated Byzantine Fault Tolerance mechanism. Furthermore, DWS will also utilize NEO’s cross-chain protocol, quantum-resistant cryptography, distributed storage protocol, and secure communication protocol.
